responses.body:
{
  "id": "{{urlParam 'submissionId'}}",
  "userId": "{{faker 'string.uuid'}}",
  "userName": "{{faker 'internet.userName'}}",
  "problemId": {{faker 'number.int' min=100 max=1000}},
  "totalScore": {{faker 'number.int' min=100 max=1000}},
  "maxTime": {{faker 'number.int' min=100 max=1000}},
  "maxMemory": {{faker 'number.float' min=100 max=1000}},
  "codeLength": {{faker 'number.float' min=100 max=1000}},
  "languageId": "{{body 'languageId'}}",
  "overallJudgeStatus": "{{oneOf (array 'AC' 'WA' 'TLE' 'CE')}}",
  "submittedAt": "{{date '2020-01-01' '2024-11-05' 'yyyy-MM-dd\'T\'HH:mm:ss.SSS\'Z\''}}",
  "judgeResults": [
    {{#repeat 3}}
    {
      "testcaseId": "{{faker 'string.uuid'}}",
      "testcaseName": "{{faker 'internet.userName'}}",
      "judgeStatus": "{{oneOf (array 'AC' 'WA' 'TLE' 'CE')}}",
      "score": {{faker 'number.int' min=100 max=1000}},
      "time": {{faker 'number.int' min=100 max=1000}},
      "memory": {{faker 'number.float' min=100 max=1000}},
    }
    {{/repeat}}
  ]
}

headers.value: Content-Type, Origin, Accept, Authorization, Content-Length, X-Requested-With
